snippet: LEAD: When 500 of the nation's earthquake specialists gathered in Sacramento in August to prepare for a shock like the one that hit Northern California today, they warned that the first hours would be a time of chaos and uncertainty....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: When 500 of the nation's earthquake specialists gathered in Sacramento in August to prepare for a shock like the one that hit Northern California today, they warned that the first hours would be a time of chaos and uncertainty.

headline.main: Chaos and Uncertainty For the Rescue Teams

byline.original: By SETH MYDANS, Special to The New York Times
